<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV117">
<l>accamnōyo ṭallaṟpaṟpi ṟappuvāya mūppivai</l>
<l>vaittacintai vaittavākkai māṟṟivāṉi lēṟṟuvā</l>
<l>ṉaccutaṉa nantakīrtti yātiyanta millava</l>
<l>ṉaccunāka ṇaikkiṭanta nātaṉvēta kītaṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>He who removes these—[namely,] fear, pain, distress, old age in the many births,</l>
<l>the thoughts that [one] has, [and] the appointed bodies, in order to lift [us] to Heaven—</l>
<l>Acyuta, He with endless glory, He without a beginning or an end,</l>
<l>the Lord who lay upon the bed that is a venomous snake</l>
<l rend="indent">is the One sung about in the Vedas!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
